WEBVTT

00:04:29.574 --> 00:04:34.948
Now imagine for just one moment
that it's you stuck in that jail cell,

00:04:34.972 --> 00:04:37.656
and you don't have
the 500 dollars to get out.

00:04:39.072 --> 00:04:43.128
And someone comes along
and offers you a way out.

00:04:44.145 --> 00:04:45.993
"Just plead guilty," they say.

00:04:46.559 --> 00:04:48.655
"You can go home back to your job.

00:04:49.182 --> 00:04:50.612
Just plead guilty.

00:04:51.003 --> 00:04:53.143
You can kiss your kids goodnight tonight."

00:04:53.503 --> 00:04:56.679
So you do what anybody
would do in that situation.

00:04:56.703 --> 00:05:00.241
You plead guilty
whether you did it or not.